headline: Is Synopsys (SNPS) Getting Pricey After Recent Volatility In Its Share Price?
summary: If you are wondering whether Synopsys at around US$437.45 is a fair deal or starting to look expensive, you are not alone in asking that question right now. The stock has been quite volatile recently, with a 4.4% gain over the last 7 days, a 16.7% decline over 30 days, a 8.9% decline year to date, and a 17.3% decline over 1 year, set against longer term returns of 16.4% over 3 years and 50.5% over 5 years.
